fr:mainmatter.html:p:
Idea: we decompose the address into a virtual page number (VPN) and offset i.e. 
\underbrace {01}_{\text {VPN}}\underbrace {110\cdots  01}_{\text {offset}}
we then maintain a datastructure to map \text {VPN} \mapsto  \text {PPN}, where the PPN is the physical page number (we divide both virtual and physical memory into pages). We call this data structure a page table.
